Well, at least you’re on the right track with the whole “not leeching” thing. You’ll probably need to put effort into this Thread if you have hopes of attracting serious Developers/Designers though. To ‘completely edit’ your Base, you’ll need some Designers who know what they’re doing, that’s for sure. I advise you to write up an Application for your potential partners to fill out.
